data.description: Welcome to this charming and exceptionally well-maintained residence, nestled within the highly sought-after Burkitt Village community in the heart of Nolensville. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a beautiful open concept floor plan, designed to allow an abundance of natural light to flood the living spaces. The bright and airy ambiance creates a welcoming atmosphere that is perfect for both daily living and entertaining. The primary bedroom is located on the main level, ensuring easy accessibility and a private retreat for homeowners. Upstairs, you'll find three additional bedrooms and a flex space that provides versatility for your lifestyle. Situated on an expansive lot, this property offers a fully fenced backyard, perfect for creating a secure and private outdoor oasis. The covered porch is a wonderful place to relax or entertain. This home is the perfect canvas, ready for a new owner to make it their own and fill it with cherished memories.
